# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# i18n: generated localizations + the untranslated-keys report. Regenerated by
# `flutter gen-l10n` (runs on `flutter pub get` because pubspec `generate: true`).
# Source of truth lives in lib/l10n/*.arb + l10n.yaml (both committed).
/lib/l10n/app_localizations*.dart
/l10n_untranslated.txt

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release
